Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:53.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}陷入迷茫的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:53.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}迷い込んだ気持ちをただ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:23:03.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}只想寻找能将我引导至出口的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:23:03.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}出口へ導く手を探していたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:07.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}Wherever you are I'll find you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.26,0:23:12.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}相牵的双手 定将长相厮守
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.26,0:23:12.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}繋いだ手はlast forever
